Author: JACOBSON
Vol / Page: 207
Edition:
Quote: We were all on a `lay` .... If you are on 1/100th when 100 tons are got, you get one, and when you are on a `lay` they find you - that's the difference between a lay and going shares. If you are on shares you find yourself.
